<br />

<br />
3rd, enchanters are less needed due to fewer "adds", and monks are less desireable as their way of "FD splitting" isn't as fast as lull pulling. 
<br />

<br />
4th, LDoN is released where there are a plethora of "2 & 3" pulls, and it is now faster, safer, and more mana efficient to pull with pacify then to handle adds even <span style="font-weight: bold">with</span> an enchanter.
<br />

<br />
5th, since Monks now have 0 desirability in an entire expansion (mediocre dps relatively, no one wants to wait for FD splitting), sony throws them a bone with an unresistable lull, so they are now accepted as pullers again. It being unresistable was actually a bug, but they decided to let it stay that way officially.
<br />

<br />
